snippet.title: Starship Simulator - Steam Teaser Video
snippet.description:
The first proper teaser video for Starship Simulator, which is a collection of very early alpha footage arranged to fit our new main theme music.

If you like what you see and you're excited about the game's future, then please consider supporting the project on Patreon. You guys truly make the magic happen!

Music by Eric E Britt @Orchestorm.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1332100/Starship_Simulator/
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/starshipsimulator
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Starship_sim
Discord: https://discord.gg/eDSQvpgdUX
